<P>By HUGH KELLY.</P>
<P>LONDON, PRINTED FOR R. BALDWIN, No. 47, PATER-NOSTER-ROW; W. JOHNSTON, No. 16, and G. KEARSLY, No. 1, in LUDGATE-STREET. M DCC LXVIII.</P>
